channel.title: Goxenar x Austin Haga - Lightning Round (Zeph Remix)
channel.description:
[Listen here](https://soundcloud.com/zephsound/goxenar-x-austin-haga)
I have been working on it for almost a year! It’s pretty crazy how far the track has come as I have been learning and teaching myself some handy things. It’s almost a completely different song than from when I worked on it the very first week. I am happy to finally be able to release a full blown track in almost 6 months of absence. I hope you guys that are a fan of dubstep, trap, riddim, etc. enjoy this track. I drew a lot of inspiration from Virtual Riot and Rickyxsan, they’ve been killing it lately.
*Creds to Goxenar & Austin for authorizing me to remix*
